<!DOCTYPE section SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<section title="Create cards with Quick Add" id="create_cards_using_quick_add">
	<p>
		Quick Add allows you to create a new card from any project page. The Quick Add button can be found on the bottom left of your browser window in the task tray.
	</p>
	<p><screenshot src="resources/images/quick_add.png"/></p>
	
	<p>
		The Quick Add button makes it easy to create cards with default values preset for the selected <cref topic="card_types">card type</cref>.
	</p>
	<p><screenshot src="resources/images/add_new_card_without_quick_add_card.png"/></p>
</section>
